==============================================================================

versions.env

Centralized, reproducible versions (pure KEY=VALUE; no bashisms).

This file should be source-able by POSIX sh, bash, dash, zsh, and env tools.



- Schema version for versions.env format; increment for breaking changes

- Example: Validate SPLUNK_VERSION in a script: [[ "${SPLUNK_VERSION}" =~ ${VERSION_PATTERN_SEMVER} ]]

==============================================================================

